Wealth Management
What we offer
Wealth Advisory
Specialist guidance on estate and succession planning


Specialist guidance on estate and succession  planning




We can help you in channelling your wealth, from domestic and international estate planning to asset protection in complex regulatory environments, including the use of structures such as trusts

Add to my collection






Looking out for your family’s assets
The structures into which you transfer your assets can have lasting consequences for you and your family. We can help you choose structures and trusts designed to protect your assets and give your family lasting benefits in an uncertain world. 

Private client and corporate expertise

Our talented Wealth Advisory team provides the one-to-one expertise you need to protect your assets. By gaining a real understanding of your requirements, we can offer you effective solutions based on our knowledge and experience of trusts law, estate preservation and investment tax relief. 
Offshore and onshore expertise

Our trust and fiduciary services are available in:

Jersey 
Guernsey 
Isle Of Man
Switzerland (Geneva)
UK onshore (Gadbrook Park)
USA (Delaware)
Singapore

Cayman Islands
India Onshore (Mumbai)

Structures tailored to your needs
We’ll draw on the full capability and expertise of Barclays to create the right structure for your trust, foundation or company. 
Integrated products
Backed by the full capability of Barclays, we adapt our structures and integrate them with credit, insurance and other solutions to meet your requirements. 






